column1: #Text=Job DescriptionHi...My Name is Ajay Singh and I'm a Resource Manager at Next Level Business Services, Inc.Please find the Job Description below and respond with an expected salary range?.
#Text=suitable time to call and contact details?.
#Text=Also, attach a copy of your updated resume.Position Title: Android DeveloperLocation: Holtsville, NYHire Type: Full Time OnlySalary: As Per MarketJob Description:- BE / B.
